org.apache.geode.experimental.driver

Class ProtobufDriver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.geode.experimental.driver.ProtobufDriver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Driver

    @Experimental
public class ProtobufDriver
extends Object
implements Driver
    Implements the behaviors of a driver for communicating with a GemFire server by way of the new protocol. This code is an experimental prototype and is presented "as is" with no warranty, suitability, or fitness of purpose implied.
